 the sources\nand the sinks of the EF. We did not find any indication of roll-type convection\nwithin penumbral filaments.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 25 Sep 2009 17:52:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-14"}
