\ncompleteness of 20%-30% for periods longer than 1 day and is complete relative\nto Hipparcos for short-period binaries.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 25 Sep 2009 20:48:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-09-29"}
